### ============================================
### Payment & Subscription Tests
### ============================================
### Prerequisites:
### 1. User must be logged in (get token from auth/login)
### 2. Replace YOUR_TOKEN_HERE with actual token
### 3. Replace YOUR_PRICE_ID with Stripe price ID
### ============================================

### Create Checkout Session
### Requires: Stripe Price ID (get from Stripe Dashboard)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/payment/create-checkout-session
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "priceId": "price_YOUR_PRICE_ID_HERE"
}

### Get Subscription Status
GET http://localhost:3000/api/payment/subscription-status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Cancel Subscription
POST http://localhost:3000/api/payment/cancel-subscription
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### Webhook Testing (Use Stripe CLI)
### ============================================
### To test webhooks locally, use Stripe CLI:
### 1. Install: https://stripe.com/docs/stripe-cli
### 2. Login: stripe login
### 3. Forward webhooks: stripe listen --forward-to localhost:3000/api/payment/webhook
### 4. Trigger test events: stripe trigger checkout.session.completed
### ============================================

